{"id":"guide/interpolation","title":"使用內嵌語法顯示值","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"displaying-values-with-interpolation\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3455c55pm1btdpu0siz9thlsj\">使用內嵌語法顯示值<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/interpolation#displaying-values-with-interpolation\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e44b21uig1fakj5vcfuvz1bdu\">前提條件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/interpolation#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"f2juqutjpadle5b16ec0pok4o\"><a href=\"guide/architecture-components\">元件基礎</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1basrmrmsgqz0ktslwd53at7b\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\">樣板基礎</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7boobbok84b51i60fmn6nurfv\"><a href=\"guide/binding-syntax\">綁定語法</a></li>\n</ul>\n<!--todo: needs a level 2 heading for info below -->\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6dygjtsu8ee0p3pcav4laccrk\">內嵌是指將表示式嵌入到被標記的文字中。預設情況下，內嵌使用雙花括號 <code>{{</code> 和 <code>}}</code> 作為定界符。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4d26pg9dxnwbmnhq0nz6ow0zz\">為了說明內嵌的工作原理，請考慮一個包含 <code>currentCustomer</code> 變數的 Angular 元件：</p>\n<code-example path=\"interpolation/src/app/app.component.ts\" region=\"customer\">\ncurrentCustomer = 'Maria';\n\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"exg0awqq6nh8pr3rv43q3b6p6\">可以用內嵌在相應的元件樣板中顯示此變數的值：</p>\n<code-example path=\"interpolation/src/app/app.component.html\" region=\"interpolation-example1\">\n&lt;h3&gt;Current customer: {{ currentCustomer }}&lt;/h3&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5el4dnyifrq5u5es3m07av8a0\">Angular 會用相應元件屬性的字串值替換掉 <code>currentCustomer</code>。在這裡，它的值是 <code>Maria</code>。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6qto1w9uuh3wjz2hfd2dkpisx\">在以下範例中，Angular 會求出 <code>title</code> 和 <code>itemImageUrl</code> 屬性的值，以顯示一些標題文字和影象。</p>\n<code-example path=\"interpolation/src/app/app.component.html\" region=\"component-property\">\n&lt;p&gt;{{title}}&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;<a href=\"api/common/NgOptimizedImage\" class=\"code-anchor\">img</a> alt=\"item\" src=\"{{itemImageUrl}}\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"whats-next\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a9eze1dnpifv7a337eeae0oi5\">下一步呢？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/interpolation#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"mfyxx87fibqbnu58gbuv5vkk\"><a href=\"guide/property-binding\">屬性繫結</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6tdxpqx0gzw605pst3e974rgi\"><a href=\"guide/event-binding\">事件繫結</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：Fri Sep 01 2023</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/ajs-quick-reference\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/binding-syntax\n - guide/event-binding\n - guide/example-apps-list\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/property-binding\n - guide/template-overview\n - guide/template-statements\n - guide/template-syntax\n - guide/user-input\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07\n - tutorial/tour-of-heroes/toh-pt5\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/NgOptimizedImage\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/binding-syntax\n - guide/event-binding\n - guide/glossary#template\n - guide/interpolation#displaying-values-with-interpolation\n - guide/interpolation#prerequisites\n - guide/interpolation#whats-next\n - guide/property-binding\n-->"}